{"title":"Rivendell Clem Pre-Order Today at Noon PST","link":"https://theradavist.com/rivendell-clem-pre-order/","date":1738260010000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Rivendell Clem Smith epitomizes the Grant Petersen “Hilly Bike” ethos. It’s got a long <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/esker-cycles-hayduke-lvs-longtail-review/\" target=\"_blank\">W-factor</a> (distance from the middle of the saddle to the rear axle of a bicycle), clearance for 29er tires on the large size and 27.5 wheels on the other two sizes, a gracious standover, fender, and rack mounts, and is by far the most unique looking bicycle the brand has ever produced.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_02.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_02.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/2025_Rivendell_Clem_Pre-Order_02.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>These tig-welded frames are built with <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/eisentraut-mountain-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">investment-cast</a> Rivendell lugs and are simply stunning. They come in the option to buy a Taiwan-built complete for $2,400 at a significant savings or have the boyz at Rivendell custom build you one starting at $3,136. You can build one yourself, too for <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/frame-clem-2025?mc_cid=861482e662&amp;mc_eid=081ebe17bd\" target=\"_blank\">$1,400 as a frameset</a>.</p>\n<p>Roll on over to <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/clem-completes-2025?mc_cid=861482e662&amp;mc_eid=081ebe17bd\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell</a> to get on the pre-order today at 12 noon PST.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/rivendell-clem-pre-order/\">Rivendell Clem Pre-Order Today at Noon PST</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"af4143c59c6a9576a8ac5eb846ba202adfb16f5a578d4d72003549bdebd31cc1","category":"Cycling"}